  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table bordercolor=\"#000080\">\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>They\n        were...</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>From Alfred Tennyson's \"The\n        Sisters\". Note that Tennyson's poem reads 'she'\n        instead of 'he.' </font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Sisters_AT.htm\">Tennyson's\n                The Sisters</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Sisters_AT.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><font>\"The Sisters\" and\n                \"Burbank\"</font></td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Structural analysis</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
